Prediction Workflow
User submits a ticket.
Text is cleaned and transformed.
Features are extracted.
The trained model predicts the category.
The ticket is routed to the relevant department.
Prediction confidence is recorded.
Confidence Score Generation

Most classifiers produce probabilities for each class. The highest probability becomes the predicted category, while the probability itself serves as a confidence score.

Example:

Technical Support: 0.92
Billing: 0.05
Account Issues: 0.03

Predicted category: Technical Support (92% confidence)

