Conclusion

TicketSense demonstrates how modern helpdesk systems combine web technologies, databases, and machine learning to automate ticket classification and routing. By leveraging Flask for the backend, HTML/CSS/JavaScript for the frontend, SQLite for data storage, and text classification algorithms for intelligent routing, the system improves operational efficiency, reduces manual effort, and enhances customer support. The project provides a strong foundation for future enhancements such as AI-powered prioritization, cloud deployment, and omnichannel support.

